# Why does the site use Creative Commons?

This repository is mostly comprised of information and not as much code. The majority of the content here is copied directly from Wikipedia, and
the content that is not copied is still kept under CC BY-SA for convenience. All we request is a line of credit if any of our content is used.

The logo uses CC BY-ND to stop people from changing it. Just use the logo! We couldn't care less, we always have more important things to do
than pursue people for using the logo we designed.
